Besieged;;80;;74;;R;;Mild-mannered composer Jason Kinsky (David Thewlis) hires Shandurai (Thandie Newton), a medical student and recent immigrant from Africa, to work as a part-time maid in his home. As the repressed maestro observes his intoxicating new employee, Shandurai reveals herself to be a free spirit with a captivating sadness. And, when Kinsky suddenly declares his undying love for her, she sends him on a dark journey into the depths of passion, jealousy and political intrigue.;;Drama;;Bernardo Bertolucci;;1998;;Thandiwe Newton,David Thewlis,Claudio Santamaria,Massimo De Rossi,Cyril Nri,Paul Osul,Veronica Lazar,Alexander Menis;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/besieged